/228990/original.jpeg?1511430651',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(96,'Jamming With Edward','1','9','The Bebop crew tries to crack the case of mysterious satellite drawings appearing on the Earth\'s surface, but they\'ll need help from a hacker know as Radical Edward to earn their bounty!','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/228989/original.jpeg?1511430651',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(97,'Wild Horses','1','19','While Spike pays a visit to the man who built his ship, Faye and Jet go fishing for space pirates.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/228987/original.jpeg?1511430650',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(98,'Pierrot Le Fou','1','20','Spike takes a beating during a chance encounter with an indestructible assassin. While Jet searches for the secret to the madman\'s power, Spike goes looking for payback!','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/228986/original.jpeg?1511430650',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(99,'Boogie Woogie Feng Shui','1','21','Spurred by a cryptic email, Jet goes looking for an old friend, but finds his daughter – and a mysterious sun stone – instead.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/228985/original.jpeg?1511430649',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(100,'Black Dog Serenade','1','16','Jet teams up with a former partner to settle the score with the man who took his arm, but he soon discovers that memories can be deceiving.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/228984/original.jpeg?1511430649',1,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(101,'Time to Tell','1','26','Robin and Amon finally confront Zaizen and learn the truth about Robin\'s existence. To Zaizen\'s surprise, instead of being traumatized, Robin is instead strengthened with resolve. Now Robin and Amon must stop Zainzen\'s final solution for the sake of both Witches and Humans alike.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/79/original.jpg?1416320883',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(102,'Redemption Day','1','25','Robin\'s mentor from Italy, Father Juliano, has made a sudden visit to Japan to see her. She confronts him about her real identity; who, or what, is she? Father Juliano gently revels to Robin her own true nature. Meanwhile, the STN-J Team and Nagira plan to stage an assault on the Factory.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/78/original.jpg?1416320881',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(103,'Sympathy for the Devil','1','23','Zaizen is trying to develop a new type of Orbo that would allow ordinary humans to hunt Witches, but it has disturbing side effects. Amon meets with Robin but does not attack her; instead he reveals more about his orders. Dojima and Nagira follow a Factory assault van but the target is Sakaki!','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/76/original.jpg?1416320876',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(104,'Family Portrait','1','22','Suspicions about Zaizen\'s motives for Orbo leads Headquarters to cut funding by 40%. Nevertheless, Zaizen pushes ahead with his plan. Meanwhile, Robin and Nagira visit an old woman that was recently seen with Amon. When the woman is shocked to see Robin, they find out why; she has a photograph of a girl that resembles Robin in one of her bedrooms. Further investigations lead them closer to the truth behind Robin\'s past, as a link between genetics and Witches appears.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/75/original.jpg?1416320872',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(105,'Missing','1','19','When Nagira brings in a couple to consult about the Fragment, Robin is unnerved by the woman\'s strange behavior. Her husband later explains that Robin resembles their missing daughter, whom they believe was Hunted by the Factory. Having being brought up without parents, the woman\'s reaction stirs up forgotten feelings within Robin and she begins to seek a relationship with the couple.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/72/original.jpg?1416320866',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(106,'Dilemma','1','17','As Robin bides her time hiding from the Factory, she takes on two jobs: as a bike messenger for Nagira\'s Law Firm and as a babysitter for an unusual girl. While delivering packages one day, she spots Dojima being attacked by a Witch and his gang. After saving Dojima, she learns that the STN-J is seriously undermanned. Dojima begs Robin for help. Can Robin risk being exposed to the Factory by helping her friends at the STN-J?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/70/original.jpg?1416320857',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(107,'Loaded Guns','1','14','While on a case with Amon, Robin is ambushed by an unseen attacker. Later, back at the STN-J, Michael discovers that the shell casting left behind came from anti-Witch bullets. The weapon that could fire such bullets has not been used by the STN-J in five years. Who could be Hunting Robin?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/67/original.jpg?1416320850',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(108,'The Eyes of Truth','1','13','Robin is surprised to learn that the Inquisitor who tested her has arrived in Japan to test a new potential Hunter. As Robin watches the Inquisitor test the candidate, Shiro Masuda, she is reminded of her own inquisition. She finds that there is a thin line between being a Hunter or a Witch. Masuda must now choose which side he will join, and accept the consequences of his decision.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/66/original.jpg?1416320849',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(109,'Sign of the Craft','1','9','When two bodies are found apparently burned from the inside out, attention is drawn to Robin; whoever did this has the same power she has. A girl named Aki Yoshioka is the best suspect, but when the STN-J investigates they only find a pile of sand and a confession to killing three people on Aki\'s computer. Is the team chasing a ghost?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/62/original.jpg?1416320840',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(110,'Simple-Mind','1','7','When a suspected thief\'s wrecked car is pulled from the harbor, the STN-J suspect there is more going on then a mere accident. When the go to question the suspect, however, he flees in his car, crushing Karasuma\'s vehicle with a powerful blow in the process. But, was it the thief doing the crushing or a more sinister force?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/60/original.jpg?1416320836',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(111,'Raindrops','1','6','When Robin\'s Vespa runs out of gas during a rainstorm, she is picked up by a kind-hearted motorist. Shortly after dropping Robin off, the woman is killed in a horrible accident. Upset over her death, Robin senses that a Witch may have been involved. Together with Amon, Robin pushes forward to uncover the truth.','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/59/original.jpg?1416320834',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(112,'Smells Like the Wandering Spirit','1','5','While searching a shanty town for a potential Witch, Sakaki investigates an oddly agitated man. When the man suddenly flees from him in terror, Sakaki chases after him and inadvertently causes terrified man to run into traffic and struck by a truck. An autopsy reveals the man wasn\'t a  Witch after all; just a normal man with the scent of olives. The question remains: Why did he run when he had no apparent reason to?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/58/original.jpg?1416320831',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(113,'Stubborn Aesthetics','1','4','When Amon hands Robin the file for unsolved and possibly Witch related murder cases, she finds a string of deaths that occurred in the very same park she walks through to go to church. There is a young girl who paints landscapes there every day and Robin becomes concerned for her safety. She teams up with Ms. Karasuma to investigate the park, but is she sure the murders were caused by a Witch?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/57/original.jpg?1416320828',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(114,'Dancing in Darkness','1','3','The STN-J is called in by the local police when a dried corpse is found. When Robin finds a dead insect on the body the team goes on a hunt for a Witch who can control insects. They find that there were two previous victims found in the same condition. The cases point to a similar rash of deaths leading back hundreds of years.  Apparently, all the dead are Witches. Is the STN-J dealing with an immortal who feeds on Witches?','25',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/56/original.jpg?1416320826',4,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(115,'Episode 969','1','969','','24',NULL,NULL,12,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(116,'Episode 968','1','968','','24',NULL,NULL,12,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(117,'A Terrifying Mysterious Power! Captain Buggy, the Clown Pirate!','1','5','In order to save herself and steal a map to the Grand Line, Nami tricks Luffy into allowing her to turn him over to Buggy. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/103486/original.jpg?1523923585',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(118,'Morgan versus Luffy! Who\'s the Mysterious Pretty Girl?','1','3','Luffy convinces Zoro to join his crew, but they must first defeat Captain Morgan. After freeing the island from Morgan\'s oppressive rule, Coby is accepted as a marine while the other two continue on their journey. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/103484/original.jpg?1523923584',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:54','2018-04-17 19:10:54'),(119,'Episode 967','1','967','','24',NULL,NULL,12,'