ut in a hopeless position after all three members ended up getting only eggs. But Azuma pulls through by asking for a certain type of flour and makes Japan# 21. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/1028/original.jpg?1416323950',19,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(413,'Before the Finals!! A Dark Shadow Approaches Kazuma','1','22','The episode begins with a short over-view of the past few episodes. Kawachi is also suggested by Matsushiro to go train at a church during the finals, before facing Suwabara. After talking to Kanmuri in the kitchen, Yukino finds the petalite stone and then breaks it in sand pouring it into a sandbox. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/1018/original.jpg?1416323910',19,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(414,'The Best Possible Team!! We\'re Going to Win with Onono Komachi-san!','1','15','In a hopeless situation, Azuma becomes depressed. Meanwhile Kawachi goes on to win his match, and gives Azuma an idea. The day of the match between Azuma and Shachihoko has arrived. Azuma ends up winning by making an okonomiyaki-style sandwich on pannini bread. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/1011/original.jpg?1416323886',19,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(415,'This is the Path I Must Take!? The Road of the Loquat!','1','68',NULL,'24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/1064/original.jpg?1416324073',19,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(416,'Mysterious Brothers !! Kaizer\'s Natural Shape!','1','42','Team Japan begins to prepare for their match against Kayser. On the scheduled day of the match, Kayser reveals their true form, while the match has started, Azuma has yet to arrive. During this episode, Suwabara\'s Lupan #6 is revealed, as well as Gran\'s special blue dough, that will be made into the perfect bread for F1 racing, while Suwabara\'s bread has a fatal flaw. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/1038/original.jpg?1416323981',19,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(417,'Compromising Positions','1','11','After Junko double-crosses Desert Punk, he takes her prisoner and locks both of them inside a secret desert hide-out. Angry, Junko knocks Desert punk in the head, and now he can\'t remember the code to let them out.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/162339/original.jpg?1416170072',16,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(418,'A Raw Deal','1','20','Desert Punk discovers that Stryker, Natsuko and many others are all part of the Underground Mercenaries, a group taht wants to overthrow the government.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/162417/original.jpg?1416170084',16,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(419,'Hidden Agendas','1','22','Kosuna is hired to guard a secret meeting of the Underground Mercenaries Union.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/162432/original.jpg?1416170086',16,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(420,'The Dog In Heat','1','8','Desert Punk and Kosuna have a new job: to destroy a stone, believed to be cursed. The only problem is, the curse seems to be real, and everything that can go wrong, does go wrong.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/162296/original.jpg?1416170068',16,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(421,'The Throne of Roses II: The Refuge','1','21','The Pope takes refuge with the vampires who have been living underground and helping in Albion\'s prosperity. The members of AX and the rebel vampires race to find The Pope. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/954/original.jpg?1416320854',18,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(422,'The Night Lords II: Twilight Of The Capital','1','16','Abel and Asta head to the Empress’ palace for the meeting in an attempt to free Ion of his bad name. Meanwhile, Ion and Esther search for Menmaru. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/949/original.jpg?1416320842',18,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(423,'The Iblis II: Betrayal Blaze','1','13','Sister Esther, Ion and Radu flee from the execution squad, in an attempt to meet with Lady Caterina. Father Abel and Sister Esther try to help Ion and Radu escape, but Radu betrays them. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/946/original.jpg?1416320837',18,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(424,'Sword Dancer','1','6','A murder on holy ground has taken place in Amsterdam, and Lady Caterina sends in the mysterious Father Hugue de Watteau, also known as \"Sword Dancer\", to investigate. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/939/original.jpg?1416320817',18,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(425,'Mizuki\'s Scenario','1','30','The intense doubles match goes long, and Kaido finds that his snake is ineffective against the St. Rudolph duo. The pressure pushes Kaido to the brink and a new move is unleashed.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/701/original.jpeg?1416583276',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(426,'The Moon Volley','1','31','Next up is Seigaku’s “golden pair,” Kikumaru and Oishi, and the two find themselves facing some tough challengers. Ryoma notices that their opponent Akazawa’s hits make the ball a blur—could this be the secret to their surprising success?','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/702/original.jpeg?1416583275',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(427,'The Boomerang Snake','1','16','Eiji Kikumaru and Shuichiro Oishi win their doubles match over Fudomine, and Kaoru Kaido begins his match against Fudomine’s Akira Kamio. Kaido is pushed by Akira’s speedy game and is forced to use his specialty “Snake Shot,” but he slips!','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/687/original.jpeg?1416583274',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(428,'A Little Gesture of Triumph','1','17','Kaido’s new move “The Boomerang Snake” ends up amazing everyone and himself! He regains his confidence and restarts his strategy—to tenaciously wear down a player and finish them off with one strike.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/688/original.jpeg?1416583273',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(429,'The Love Letter','1','18','Ryoma starts his match with Fudomine’s Shinji Ibu, and Coach Ryuzaki remembers when Ryoma’s father Nanjiro was a student of hers.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/689/original.jpeg?1416583272',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(430,'Battle-Scarred Ryoma','1','19','Ryoma injures his eye as he tries to bounce back from a series of shots from Shinji Ibu. Ibu’s shots were strategically chosen to momentarily paralyze Ryoma. Ryoma isn’t giving up despite his injury...','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/690/original.jpeg?1416583271',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(431,'Kaoru\'s Troubles','1','22','It’s after practice. Kaoru goes off to train but Ryoma, Momo, Horio, Kachiro and Katsuo go shopping for supplies.  On their way, they run into a purse-snatcher. Momo “borrows” a bike and chases the culprit.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/693/original.jpeg?1416583269',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(432,'Here Comes Inui\'s Deluxe Drink!','1','23','It’s nine days away from the Metropolitan Tournament! Captain Tezuka and Inui introduce a new way to train. The team members are separated based on their style of play and rally against each other...','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/694/original.jpeg?1416583268',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(433,'Ryoma\'s Day Off','1','24','Coach Ryuzaki asks Ryoma to take Sakuno to restring her racket, but everybody else thinks he’s taking her out on a date!','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/695/original.jpeg?1416583267',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(434,'The Hard Day','1','9','Ryoma defeats Sadaharu and wins a spot on the regular team. Sadaharu isn’t out of the picture though—he stays on to help train the regulars and introduce them to his special concoction: a vegetable drink guaranteed to make them stronger.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/680/original.jpeg?1416583266',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(435,'Counterattack! Sasabe Again?','1','10','Sasabe has returned! Only this time it’s his father who’s the troublemaker, making a fun day at Kachiro’s father’s tennis club a nightmare. Ryoma tries to diffuse the situation slyly by asking Mr. Sasabe to teach him tennis.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/681/original.jpeg?1416583265',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(436,'Ryoma Vs. Momoshiro','1','11','Ryoma and Momo are developing a competitive friendship. They both have their eyes on the #3 doubles spot so they decide to play each other for it. At the outdoor tennis courts they come upon a round-robin doubles game.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/682/original.jpeg?1416583264',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(437,'The Triple Counter','1','14','The mysterious team from Fudomine Junior High comes out of nowhere to defeat a seeded school. Shusuke Fuji and Taka Kawamura are up to play them in doubles.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/685/original.jpeg?1416583262',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(438,'To Each His Own Battle','1','15','Fudomine’s Ishida breaks out his secret weapon—the “Wave Surge” shot—to bring the momentum back to their team. As Shusuke prepares to return the invincible flat shot meant for him, Taka steps in and intercepts it.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/686/original.jpeg?1416583261',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(439,'Samurai Jr.','1','2','Ryoma’s first day at Seishun Academy, also known as “Seigaku.” He rescues Horio, a seventh grader being picked on by two older tennis team members. He easily dispatches them, piquing the interest of Takeshi Momoshiro, a tennis team regular.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/673/original.jpeg?1416583259',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(440,'The Seigaku Regulars Make Their Debut!','1','3','Arai tries to get his revenge on Ryoma. He hides Ryoma’s rackets and challenges him to a match, forcing him to play with an old and broken racket. All the while the Seigaku team members observe Ryoma closely.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/674/original.jpeg?1416583258',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(441,'The One Named Viper','1','4','Ryoma has been chosen by Captain Kunimitsu Tezuka to play for a spot on the regular team, a first for a seventh grader. His main opponent is Kaoru Kaido, infamous for his “Snake Shot” and reptilian nature.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/675/original.jpeg?1416583257',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(442,'The Snake Shot','1','5','Ryoma patiently plays Kaido’s game while gathering information crucial to voiding his dangerous “Snake Shot.” Ryoma counters effectively, amazing all who watch.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/676/original.jpeg?1416583256',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(443,'Nanjiro Echizen','1','6','Mr. Inoue from Monthly Pro Tennis magazine goes to interview Ryoma’s quirky and lazy father Nanjiro. Rebuffing his questions, Nanjiro challenges Inoue to a game of tennis.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/677/original.jpeg?1416583255',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(444,'The Two Ryomas','1','7','Ryoma’s next opponent in the ranking matches is Sadaharu Inui, a scientific and methodical tennis player whose data never fails him.','22',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/678/original.jpeg?1416583254',13,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(445,'Karen\'s Love, Still a Long Way to Go! Karen\'s Love, Little by Little! Karen\'s Love, And Then...','1','18','Karen\'s Love, Still a Long Way to Go!:  Ichijou remembers the date that Imadori promised her, but Imadori doesn\'t recall it at all.Karen\'s Love, Little by Little!:  Ichijou\'s date with Imadori has been set, but unfortunately, Ichijou also has a wrestling match on the same day as her date.  But, never fear!  Tenma\'s here!','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/879/original.jpg?1416326650',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(446,'Nara! Karasuma! Harima!','1','11','Nara!:  Tenma and her girl friends spend the day at a water amusement park, where they meet a group of boys who want to go out with them.  One of those boys is Nara Kentarou, who secretly likes Tenma.Karasuma!:  On a rainy day, Tenma goes to a bus stop where she meets Karasuma.  She worries if Karasuma doesn\'t like her after that curry incident.','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/872/original.jpg?1416326628',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(447,'First Grocery Shopping! First Boxed Lunch! My First Heartbreak! What?','1','8','First Grocery Shopping!:  Eri goes grocery shopping for the first time.  She\'s buying ingredients for a dinner she is making.First Boxed Lunch!:  Tenma makes a boxed lunch with curry inside so that she can eat with Karasuma, since curry is his favorite food.','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/869/original.jpg?1416326621',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(448,'Pigs Say Oink Oink! Cats Say Meow! Frogs and Kappas Say Ribbit Ribbit Ribbit!','1','4','Pigs Say Oink Oink!:  It\'s time for a school field trip.  Tenma aims to sit next to Karasuma, whereas Harima wants to sit next to Tenma.  Unfortunately, Harima gets on the wrong bus and ends up in a truck full of pigs.Cats Go Meow!:  Yakumo tries to care for a stray black cat.  She also meets Hanai Haruki, who is deeply in love with her.','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/865/original.jpg?1416326611',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(449,'Fretfulness Hesitation Wandering','1','24','Fretfulness:  There are rumors going around the school about Harima and Eri dating each other.  Since Harima knows that he no longer has a chance with Tenma, he asks Yakumo to get something from off his desk and change the nametag on it.  The thing was supposed to be Harima\'s love story, but Yakumo accidently picks up a shirt that was meant to be a present for Harima from Eri, who ends up thinking that Yakumo is dating Harima.Hesitation:  Karasuma\'s birthday is coming up soon.  So Tenma tries her best to bake a cake for him.','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/885/original.jpg?1416326666',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(450,'Hanai Strikes Back! Karen Shines! Onee-san, Revisited!','1','21','Hanai Strikes Back!:  Hanai returns from his training and learns that Harima Kenji has just saved two girls from a gang.  Hanai rushes to where Harima was last seen.  He finds that an entire gang has been beaten up, but it was not Harima Kenji who did it.  Instead, it was.. Harry MacKenzie?Karen Shines!:  Lala decides to have lunch with Ichijou, but things go bad when Imadori starts provoking Lala.  Also, class 2-D\'s Harry MacKenzie and Tougou Masakazu challenge class 2-C at the upcoming sports festival.','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/882/original.jpg?1416326659',15,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(451,'Project D','4','1','The long awaited 4th stage finally arrives and in it we learn that Ryosuke Takahashi has formed his new racing  team \"\"Project D\"\" consisting of his hand picked Double Aces his brother Keisuke Takahashi with his Mazda RX-7 FD3S and of course Takumi Fujiwara with his Toyota AE86 Sprinter Trueno.\n\n\n\n\nIn Act 1 we learn that Project D has been undefeated so far into there campaign to become the greatest team in japan not only that but they have also been setting record times wherever they go. They\'re opponents for the first two act\'s are a team called The Seven-Star Leaf and that they will have to deal with a Mazda Miata NA6C on the downhill and a Nissan Skyline ER34 on the uphill.','27',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/353/original.jpg?1416321903',9,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(452,'The 85s\' Thunderous Turbo','4','7','A New nightmarish opponent arrives on Mt. Akina challenging Takumi in a downhill battle. Also, Itsuki gets a new upgrade for his Eight-Five as it is demonstrated on the downhill.','27',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/359/original.jpg?1416321929',9,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(453,'Last Drive','4','18','While his FD is in the shop being upgraded, Keisuke and Kyoko go out on a date. Afterwords, Keisuke testdrives his FD, as his acceleration skills has finally paid off in unleashing this new vehicle’s monstrous power','27',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/370/original.jpg?1416321965',9,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(454,'Motivation','4','13','The rain continues to pour down towards the next battle where Keisuke’s FD competes against Wataru’s newly upgraded Eight-Six. Instead, it only gets far more intense and time consuming if it keeps raining harder and harder.','27',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/365/original.jpg?1416321954',9,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(455,'Kobayakawa Sena','1','79','Before the match, Sena removes his helmet to reveal his identity to the world. Mamori accepts who Sena is. The game against the Bando Spiders begins. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/210/original.jpg?1416321005',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(456,'The One That Waits Previously','1','78','Mamori tries to help Sena, and Sena can\'t find enough time to change into Eyeshield 21! So after school, he practices by himself by the riverside. After catching a cold because of training in the rain, Sena is forced to stay home during the Ojou vs. Gunmen game. Deciding to go, he manages to get there about halfway through the game, when Riku and Shin are in a showdown, but problems start when Mamori spots him and urges him to go home. Then, shy Sena says the words that Mamori was sure she would never hear: \"Leave me alone! I want to be here right now!\" ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/209/original.jpg?1416321000',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(457,'Come Back! Musashi!','1','76','Deimon realizes that they will need a kicker to win their game against the Bando Spiders. Sena and Monta try and convince Musashi to rejoin their team; he reveals that he quit the team to take care of his father and their construction company. In the end, he promises to rejoin once his father recovers. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/207/original.jpg?1416320995',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(458,'Spider\'s Threat','1','75','The Bando Spiders play against the Oujou White Knights. The Spiders are in the lead due to Kotarou\'s kick. Deimon is stunned that a small Bando player can take down Otawara and the team seems to know Oujou\'s passing routes. However, in the end, Oujou wins 14 to 3 and are set to play the Wild Gunmen. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/206/original.jpg?1416320994',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(459,'A Rival\'s Promise','1','74','After losing to the Seibu Gunmen, Tetsuma saves Monta from getting Deimon suspended from playing. Hiruma reveals there is a seat left in the Tokyo Tournament so they still have a chance to be in the Christmas Bowl. Deimon attends a summer festival. Mamori invites Riku. Riku tells Sena to promise to remove his eyeshield mask before the Kantou Tournament. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/205/original.jpg?1416320990',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(460,'Fated Kick','1','73','Kid tells Hiruma that he fell directly into his trap, and that everything is always too good to be true. Hiruma reminds Kid that he told him that Eyeshield would definitely win, and Kid tells Hiruma not to forget that he said Hiruma Youichi is the best quarterback in the league. They part ways, saying that the rest of the battle will be a battle of wits, and Hiruma decides to do an onside kick. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/204/original.jpg?1416320987',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(461,'Pride Of Speed Of Light','1','72','There are 9 minutes left in the game, and Deimon is behind by 9. They try to make up the difference, but Sena cannot get past Riku. With only 1 minute left, Sena finally gets past Riku\'s Rodeo Drive and scores a touchdown. Deimon is only behind by 3 points. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/203/original.jpg?1416320984',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(462,'Deimon High School Sports Meet!!','1','65','The whole Deimon team goes to a sports meeting where the team is divided into two teams, Mamori san, Hiruma, and Yukimitsu (the smart team) vs everyone else on the football team (the brawn team). They play tug-o-war and other sports. The \"brawn team\" finally finds out that Hiruma has plotted all the sports games to teach the team how to do the \"bump\" in his evil plotting ways by handcuffing everyone\'s hands (a trick first used by the Taiyo Sphinxes team). ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/196/original.jpg?1416320963',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(463,'The Man Possessing Speed Of Light Appears!?','1','64','Riku appears and talks about his past and how Sena could run because of him. Riku asks Sena who he thinks is the best player. His answer? Shin. He then asks why and Sena says because \"his power and speed are incredible.\" Riku is part of Seibu who missed the game before due to his pride. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/195/original.jpg?1416320960',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(464,'Offense And Defence 30 cm!!','1','63','Sena breaks through Kakei\'s Moby Dick Anchor, but he is stopped just inches from the touchdown by a desperate Mizumachi. Hiruma uses their last timeout with two seconds remaining and the Devil Bats behind by five points. They decide to have Sena jump over their line in a joint combination with Monta so that he goes twice as high. The plan succeeds, and they score a touchdown, winning the game. Kakei tells Sena that it no longer matters whether he is the original Eyeshield 21 or not, but that what matters is that he is one of the most excellent players Kakei has ever seen, and that Sena is Eyeshield 21. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/194/original.jpg?1416320956',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(465,'Terror! Moby Dick Anchor','1','62','The Poseidons reveal a new formation called High Wave. Hiruma immediately spots its weakness, but Sena cannot get past Kakei. The ball is turned over to Kyoshin, and they score a touchdown, giving them a five-point lead. They try to get an extra two points, but due to Hiruma\'s plan, the ball is intercepted by Monta. With 1 minute left in the game, Deimon\'s only hope is for Sena to get past Kakei. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/193/original.jpg?1416320954',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(466,'Time That Began To Move','1','83','Musashi arrives just in time and scores a 45-yard field goal, and Deimon is now only behind by eleven points. Towards the end of the episode, a strong wind arises, confusing the players. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/214/original.jpg?1416321018',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(467,'The Devil\'s Counterattack','1','71','Trying to prove to Sena that he is the better player, Riku fumbles the ball. Sena intercepts it and runs straight to a touchdown. With Deimon only down by 2, Seibuu gives the ball to Riku. Sena tries to stop him, but Riku gets by him easily, scoring another touchdown for Seibuu. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/202/original.jpg?1416320979',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(468,'Field Of Desperation','1','69','Unable to stop Kid\'s Quick and Fire technique, the Devil Bats decide to reveal the fruit of their bump training. Seibuu counters by bringing in the Iron Horse, Tetsuma. Monta is unable to stop him, and he scores a touchdown, with the extra point successful, making the score 14-6. Hiruma tries to trick Kid into a quick pass by using a Zone Blitz, but he fails and Kid rushes to a touchdown. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/200/original.jpg?1416320974',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(469,'Fastest Proof','1','68','The game against the Wild Gunmen begins. Doburoku tells the Devil Bats that if they lose concentration for even a second, they will surely lose. Deimon kicks off the ball first and it is received by Riku. He shows the power of his technique, the Rodeo Drive, by running straight to a touchdown. However, when Seibuu kicks off to Deimon, Sena returns the favor by doing the same, running a straight touchdown, being stopped by Riku just a second too late. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/199/original.jpg?1416320971',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(470,'The Man Who Knows 21','1','57','When Monta and Sena are sent to spy on the Poseidons\' final practice before the game, they are caught, and Kakei tells Sena that he wants to challenge Eyeshield 21 from the Devil Bats and prove to him that he will never match up to the \"real\" Eyeshield 21. Sena gets past him using the Devil Bat Ghost, but Hiruma, who had been watching, tells Sena that it was not Kakei\'s true strength he was running against. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/188/original.jpg?1416320935',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(471,'Wall Of The Physique Difference','1','55','After being told by Mizumachi from the Poseidons that he is no good at football, Komosubi runs away from him. He thinks that because he is short, he is useless to the Devil Bats. Everyone goes looking for him and they convince him to return home. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/186/original.jpg?1416320929',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(472,'The Control Tower Which Disappeared','1','54','At the end of the first quarter Mamori opens the game plan Hiruma gave her, which shows that Hiruma predicted every single thing that happened in the first quarter. At last Hiruma appears. The Devil Bats win the game with the help of Hiruma\'s Devil plans. Hiruma confirms his new slave after the game. \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/185/original.jpg?1416320926',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(473,'Clash! Cameleon vs Poseidon','1','52','Chamelon and Poseidon start their game. Poseidon has a great advantage because they have tall players. On the other hand the Chameleon team is disunited. Habashira\'s team gave up halfway through. Habashira tries to encourage them and force his team to win, but fails. In the end Rui confronts Hiruma and cries out through his tears, \"WHAT WAS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN YOU AND ME!\" \n','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/183/original.jpg?1416320920',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(474,'Danger! The Lethal Cameleon','1','51','Eyeshield 21 enters the Chameleons\' locker room and cuts up all their uniforms in the middle of the night. Sena said he did not do it. The Chameleons enter Deimon and try and find Eyeshield 21. They find out the Scorpions were impersonating Eyeshield. ','23',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/182/original.jpg?1416320915',6,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(475,'A Certain Decision','1','30','Suspecting foul play in Robert\'s \'accidental\' death fall, Dr. Reichwen makes some discoveries in his investigations. But as he later realizes, his investigations may have put him in harms way.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/406/original.jpg?1416325214',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(476,'Execution','1','29','Robert delves into Johan\'s past and makes a shocking discovery. Dr. Gillen speaks to Peter Jurgens, a serial murderer about Johan\'s possible involvement and gets a tragic reply. Johan confronts Robert about Stephen Joos. And Dr. Reichwen receives tragic news from the police.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/405/original.jpg?1416325211',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(477,'Evidence','1','27','Richard\'s past and present situation is revealed. Johan continues to bond with the Schuwald family and his intention is revealed.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/403/original.jpg?1416325207',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(478,'Secret Forest','1','26','A man who claims to be the son of a millionaire has committed suicide, and a detective is determined to solve the case.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/402/original.jpg?1416325203',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(479,'The Thursday Boy','1','25','Karl Neumann and Lotte Frank are both students who read latin to Hans Georg Schubert. Lotte attempts to assist Karl in finding out his past while trying to figure out the identity of a boy who reads to Schubert on Thursdays. When they both discover who he is, they find the boy, Edmund Farren, in his dormitory, dead. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/401/original.jpg?1416325200',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(480,'Lunge\'s Trap','1','22','Lunge determines that the murder of a wealthy, middle-aged, childless couple does not fit the usual modus operandi of the serial murders and decides to use this opportunity to lure Tenma to a trap. However, before he can arrest him, Lunge is critically wounded by the real criminal. Tenma is able to treat Lunge\'s injuries.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/398/original.jpg?1416325192',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(481,'Petra and Schumann','1','13','In a small village, Dr. Schumann worries over the health of his sick but stubborn old friend, Petra.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/389/original.jpg?1416325172',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(482,'The Past That Was Erased','1','10','Tenma encounters a burglar named Heckel who claims to have seen the killer. It soon results in Heckel leading Tenma to a couple of murderers.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/386/original.jpg?1416325160',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(483,'An Old Soldier and a Young Girl','1','9','An old mercenary soldier named Hugo is interrogated by Lunge about a student of his — a doctor named Tenma.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/385/original.jpg?1416325156',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(484,'A Meager Little Experiment','1','12','Dieter is picked up by Hartmann before Tenma could return, and Tenma learns more about the experiments in Kinderheim 511.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/388/original.jpg?1416325168',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(485,'Ruhenheim','1','68','With a postcard obtained by Lipsky, Lunge arrives in Ruhenheim. There he meets up with Grimmer, whose research has led him to this town as well. A working-class couple in this town realize they win the lottery and fearing that everyone else wants to kill them, the husband buys an arsenal of weapons. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/444/original.jpg?1416325329',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(486,'The Magnificent Steiner\'s Rage','1','71','Tenma runs into Lunge, the latter apologizing for his previous accusations against Tenma. Nina and Dr. Gillen rush to Ruhenheim. After the winning lottery couple is wounded in an attack on Bonaparta\'s hotel, Grimmer rushes out to the streets to reason with the unknown assailants.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/447/original.jpg?1416325338',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(487,'The Baby\'s Depression','1','64','The Baby is killed by a prostitute, and his death sends shockwaves in Petr Capek\'s organization. Capek becomes paranoid as to who is loyal or not and accidentally kills one of his guards. He makes it to his cottage where Johan is waiting for him. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/440/original.jpg?1416325319',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(488,'An Unpleasant Job','1','58','Martin, a hired hand, is hired by General Wolf\'s ex-associates to ‘take care’ of Eva. But his emotions get in the way of his orders.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/434/original.jpg?1416325304',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(489,'Decision','1','53','After hearing Roberto\'s threat against Eva, Tenma decides to confess to all charges against him so he can be placed in the same van transporting a prisoner to a Federal Penetentary as the prisoner is arranging for a jailbreak. ','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/429/original.jpg?1416325283',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(490,'The Cruelest Thing','1','49','Grimmer and Tenma tries to stop Johan from subjecting Milo, one of the orphans, to one of the most cruel fate.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/425/original.jpg?1416325264',10,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(491,'Detective Suk','1','43','A new inspector, detective Suk i