ef aboard a ship attacked by Red Foot Zeff! When the young Sanji found himself overboard, it was the fearsome captain himself who jumped to the rescue.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/172503/original.jpeg?1416583765',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(616,'The Deadly Foot Technique Bursts Forth! Sanji Vs. the Invincible Pearl!','1','25','The battle begins for possession of the Baratie, with Zeff leading the cooks against Krieg\'s pirates. Luffy and crew join the fray, but things aren\'t looking too good!','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/172502/original.jpeg?1416583763',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(617,'Protect Baratie! the Great Pirate, Red Foot Zeff!','1','23','Don Krieg promises further malice as he returns to his ship, but the threat to the Baratie proves short-lived as an even bigger threat arrives!','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/172500/original.jpeg?1416583761',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(618,'Famous Cook! Sanji of the Sea Restaurant!','1','20','The Straw Hats need a cook among their crew, so they head to a nearby restaurant and meet a passionate Sous Chef named Sanji.','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/172497/original.jpeg?1416583759',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(619,'The Terrifying Duo! Meowban Brothers Vs. Zoro!','1','13','In an effort to save Usopp\'s village, the Straw Hat Pirates seek to block the marauders\' path from the sea. With Luffy out of the battle, Zoro must face the fearsome Meowban Brothers!','24',NULL,'https://media.kitsu.io/episodes/thumbnails/172490/original.jpeg?1416583750',12,'2018-04-17 19:10:55','2018-04-17 19:10:55'),(620,'Take or Be Taken?! Showdown at the Okay Temple!','4','177','Turns out Sazanami is really a wanted criminal named Toukichi who is wanted for the murder of a family of three. Truth is however, he\'s innocent, and wants to capture the man responsible to prove 